<td colspan="3"><b><font color="#666666">Monday July 22, 2002</font></b> 
<img src="images/date.gif" height="2" width="175"> 
</td></tr>
<tr> 
<td width="5%">&nbsp;</td>
<td width="90%">
<p><font color="#0000CC" size="1">Posted by Arele</font> <br>
<b><font color="#000000">
Vulak Aerr Killed</font></b><br>
Afterlife took a nostalgic trip to the Temple of Veeshan tonight.  After disposing of Vyemm, we moved on to start the "Ring of Vulak".  During the ring, several waves of mobs are spawned.   After 2 hours and 55 minutes, our old friend Vulak spawned, and we killed him.<br>
Besides his usual treasure, Ancient Aegolism and Ancient Burnout V were discovered.<br>
Lots of pictures of the encounter have been added to our <a href="http://www.trysor.com/afterlife"><font color="#990000">scrapbook</font></a>.
<br><br>
